# Route Groups

```
src/app/
  (public)/          # All visitor-facing pages
    page.tsx         # Home / landing
    calculator/      # Multi-step zakat form
    results/         # Calculation results
    guide/           # Zakat rules & educational content
  api/               # API routes
    prices/          # Gold, silver, currency price data
  layout.tsx         # Root layout (Arabic font, RTL, theme provider)
```

- New public pages go in `src/app/(public)/`, not at the `src/app/` root.
- API routes go in `src/app/api/`.
